    "description": "<!-- MOBILE DESCRIPTION -->\n<div style=\"display:none\">\n<div vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n<span property=\"description\">Need a simple and effective solution to tent waterproofing? Use Revivex Instant Water Repellent, a spray-on formula that immediately creates a protective barrier against water, oil and stains. Pair it with Seam Grip TF or Seam Grip FC to protect your tent from top to bottom. Choose the tent “waterproofer” kit that’s right for you. Ideal for treating small and large family-size tents, Seam Grip FC seals up to 60 linear ft of seams and cures in 2-4 hours. Seam Grip TF fabric sealant also cures within 4 hours and covers up to 85 sq ft of tent floor or rainfly. From tents to boots, our multipurpose water repellent, Revivex Instant works on nylon, leather, GORE-TEX® fabric, eVent® and other waterproof-breathable materials</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- MAIN DESCRIPTION -->\n<html>\n  <head>\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n\t\t<style type=\"text/css\">\n\t\t/* FONTS AND COLORS */\n\t\tbody {\n\t\t\tfont-family: Arial,sans-serif;\n\t\t\tfont-size: 14px;\n\t\t\tline-height: 1.428571429;\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t\tbackground-color: white;\n\t\t}\n\t\th1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {\n\t\t\tcolor: black;\n\t\t}\n\t\tp {\n\t\t\twhite-space: pre-line;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.navbar a, .navbar a:active, .navbar a:hover, .navbar a:visited {\n\t\t\tcolor: #333;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.product-specs {\n\t\t\tbackground-color: #f1f1f1;\n\t\t\tpadding: 1em;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.product-specs td {\n\t\t\tfont-size:12px;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-left {\n\t\t\tmin-width:6em;\n\t\t\tfont-weight:bold;\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\t\t.attr-right {\n\t\t\tvertical-align:top;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\tdiv.footer {\n\t\t\tborder-top: 1px solid #f1f1f1;\n\t\t}\n\n\t\t.navbar-default {\n\t\t\tbackground-image: -webkit-linear-gradient(top, #ffffff 0%, #f2f2f2 100%);\n\t\t\tbackground-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff 0%, #f2f